#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>zstd</command> is a compression program."
msgstr "<command>zstd</command> je program za stiskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The zstd KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the zstd "
"KIO worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.zst</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"KIO worker za zstd ni neposredno uporaben in je namenjen, da se ga uporablja "
"kot filter, npr. KIO worker za tar lahko filtrira datoteko s pomočjo KIO "
"worker-ja za zstd, da neposredno prikaže vsebine datoteke <literal role="
"\"extension\">tar.zst</literal> v oknu &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">zst</"
"literal> extension in &konqueror;, this KIO worker is used to uncompress it "
"and display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete na datoteko, ki je stisnjena z <literal role=\"extension\">zst</"
"literal> v &konqueror;-ju, se ta KIO worker uporabi za razširjanje in jo "
"prikaže kot navadno (nestisnjeno) datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the zstd filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Če ste razvijalec in bi želeli uporabljati zstd filter, lahko najdete "
"dokumentacijo o tem, kako uporabljati KIO worker-je, na <ulink url=\"http://"
"techbase.kde.org\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/zstd\">zstd</ulink>."
msgstr "Glejte priročnik: <ulink url=\"man:/zstd\">zstd</ulink>."
